'''''Anbulla Appa''''' (English: ''Dear Father'') is a 1987 [[Tamil language|Tamil-language]] Indian drama film directed by [[A. C. Tirulokchandar]] for [[AVM Productions]]. The film stars [[Sivaji Ganesan]], [[Nadhiya]] and [[Rahman (actor)|Rahman]] in the lead roles. This was Tirulokchandar's last directorial venture before his retirement from films.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/chennai/Storyteller-who-found-his-flair-in-versatility/articleshow/52789439.cms|title=Storyteller who found his flair in versatility|last=Vamanan|first=|authorlink=Vamanan|date=2016-06-17|website=[[The Times of India]]|publisher=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|accessdate=2016-06-19}}</ref>

