== Soundtrack ==
The music was composed by [[Shankar Ganesh]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/57/3/1/1|title=Anbulla Appa LP Vinyl Records|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424045025/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F57%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref> The song "Maragathavallikku" is set in Brindavani raga.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thehindu.com/features/friday-review/music/the-power-of-three/article5075368.ece|title=The power of three|last=Mani|first=Charulatha|date=2013-08-30|work=The Hindu|access-date=13 December 2018|issn=0971-751X}}</ref>

